{"tid":1660411,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[狗竇][垃圾藍區]油塘之火不滅","createTime":"2019-10-17T13:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T17:34:59.000Z","uid":13736,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fc8e756a971a540097d6f6f57dcea4e329b7de48","tid":1660411,"uid":13736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:16:30.000Z","msg":"油塘依個地方藍到仆街就係人都知嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由6月到依家竟然無連儂牆<br />\n就連一張文宣都容納唔到呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依排油塘既手足頻頻整連儂牆<br />\n嘗試清洗油塘既 「狗除」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但啲休班狗亦都晚晚係到吠<br />\n琴晚仲吹埋雞<br />\n幾架EU豬籠衝晒入黎拉人<br />\n好在乜事都無<br />\n<br />\n油塘大本營要人！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n琴晚見到有手足寫左手靚字<br />\n「光復香港。時代革命」<br />\n即刻影低咗 見證依個時刻<br />\n但唔夠一日就已經被清潔姐姐刷走咗<br />\n仲要有狗保護住咁清理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RVoW7eg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRVoW7eg.jpg&h=77029c92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCTDA7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCTDA7C.jpg&h=63ec7a76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VMK7usD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVMK7usD.png&h=3972fd82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望係未來既日子<br />\n各位油塘既街坊可以支持下班手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以係油塘起到幅屬於<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家既連儂牆</span></span><br />\n抗衡休班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e77f777e6a45f8b9d32ea625d1a80b48e398ae6","tid":1660411,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:16:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"57bffbbd41c8382a113507a7b552cc6e99af384a","tid":1660411,"uid":13736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:17:10.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"579cf8fec70894f44e29d96e3b454007e86bf435","tid":1660411,"uid":13736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:17:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"00ca0b99afde04faa120759032b4e6037e7819a6","tid":1660411,"uid":13736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bd506548dd0822b10493c83f18d917b56bcbd1b","tid":1660411,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:45:27.000Z","msg":"各位行事小心"},{"pid":"aa54e8c260056d38547163d69acf5b5c76f63ec5","tid":1660411,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"依啲垃圾區要周圍淋油 放蟲 污染環境衛生先有用"},{"pid":"c651dd8f1cc68518541f3af02d7299e0398bf6fe","tid":1660411,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"21fec4f7aa551edbea701bb24a76dfcd6a7b0f05","tid":1660411,"uid":319235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:34:59.000Z","msg":"[和理Post] 過嚟問下啲區議員候選人喇喂<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3